high_descs: Walk to the counter by the refrigerator
Take the tomato on the counter
Turn around, walk to the sink
Put the tomato in the sink, turn on the faucet, wash the tomato with water, turn off the faucet, take the tomato out
Turn left, walk to the microwave
Open the microwave, put the tomato in
anns.task_desc: Wash the tomato, put the tomato in the microwave

high_descs: walk towards the fridge and turn right to face the kitchen counter
grab a tomato off of the counter
turn around and walk over to the kitchen sink
rinse the tomato off in the sink
move to the left a bit and look up towards the microwave
place the tomato inside the microwave and close the door
anns.task_desc: put a rinsed off tomato inside the microwave

high_descs: Move to the counter right of the fridge.
Pick up the tomato from the counter.
Bring the tomato backwards to the sink.
Wash the tomato in the sink.
Bring the tomato up to the microwave above the sink.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned tomato in the microwave.
